short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bring Jeff the Land Shark’s playful spirit to your browser with fun visuals and quick shortcuts.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Watch as Jeff the Land Shark jumps, spins, and playfully blows bubbles, bringing a sense of joy and fun to your screen.

🎨 Playful Design: A lively and quirky interface filled with Jeff's playful movements and bubbly atmosphere.
⏰ Clock and Date: Keep track of time as Jeff continues his fun antics.
🔗 Quick Access Shortcuts: Jump straight to your favorite websites with ease.
🎮 Play Games: Add a layer of fun with browser-based games inspired by Jeff's antics.
Google Search Bar: Perform fast and efficient searches with the engine selected by the user.
🚀 More Extension: Enhance your browsing experience with additional fun features based on Jeff's adventures.
